Name: Ataque Marino
About the game: Arcade game of two-dimensional shooting, in which two players can participate simultaneously. It has a system as a tribute to the arcade machines, in which you must insert your 'coin' to play. And for the challenge to be greater, you have three lives and three continues to finish the game.
